title: Braun Series 7 shaver - 100% waterproof and fully washable
description: Braun shavers have a fully sealed body and can be rinsed quickly and easily under running water. For optimal convenience, you can use the Clean & Renew™ system to hygienically clean your shaver at the touch of a button.
